title: Awakening eBook Collection #1 (Wake Up and Be Happy)
description:
This is part of my personal collection that has dramatically changed my life for the better. I have 

worked for years to wake up, and I want to share what has made me the happiest person I've ever 

been.

As I said, this is just part of my collection, but it's a wonderful start, and I'll upload more when I am 

led to do so. Or you are welcome to visit this form: http://eepurl.com/ER6vr  -- and signup, I will send 

you free ebooks from my collection every week. This is totally free, no scams, no ads, I just want to 

spread the LOVE that I have received.

Besides, you can't give without getting...it's the same thing. :) So bless me by being blessed!

eBooks contained in this volume of Awakened Way #1:

Neville Goddard - Awakened Imagination
Neville Goddard - The Power of Awareness
Awakening the Third Eye
40 Day Meditations
Joel S. Goldsmith - Meditation on GOD
The Intuitive Mind (Profiting from the Power of Your Sixth Sense)



Peace, be still. GOD BLESS.

J. Drake (Awakened1)
